version_description: We've made some general improvements & bug fixes.

Hey there to all those making beautiful Quickart!
We’re excited to bring you some more options and give you even more art to explore. Here’s what’s new in this release:
- Urban Portrait is waiting to give your selfie an urban, graffiti feel
- Glitch Portrait just may make you feel like a modern Picasso
Have more ideas that you’d love to see? Let us know!
Yours,
The Quickart Team
